query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS alert_webhook_logs (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  webhook_config_id INT NOT NULL,
  alert_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  alert_title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  alert_message TEXT,
  alert_data JSON,
  channel_type VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL,
  recipient_info VARCHAR(255),
  status ENUM('pending', 'sent', 'failed', 'rate_limited') DEFAULT 'pending' NOT NULL,
  response_code INT,
  response_body TEXT,
  error_message TEXT,
  sent_at TIMESTAMP NULL,
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (id),
  INDEX idx_webhook_config (webhook_config_id),
  INDEX idx_alert_type (alert_type),
  INDEX idx_created_at (created_at)
)
